Competition Watchdog Seeks to Block United Continental, Air Canada Venture

-- B y   T h e o p h i l o s   A r g i t i s
-- 
2011-06-27T16:28:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-27/competition-watchdog-seeks-to-block-united-continental-air-canada-venture.html
Canada’s competition watchdog is
seeking to block a joint venture between  Air Canada (AC/A)  and  United
Continental Holdings Inc. (UAL)   Canada’s competition commssioner said in a statement that
it has filed an application with the country’s competition
tribunal to prohibit the venture, because it will “monopolize”
or reduce competition on 19 routes between the two countries.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Theophilos Argitis in Ottawa at 
 targitis@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
